Since the summer of 2013, Biles had never failed in the all-around competition. As long as she wanted to, she would win.
It seems that Mustafina slight lead after her two spins is only illusory.
Simone Biles, reigning world champion of the balance beam and floor exercise, lay in wait.
She scored 15.433 on the balance beam, and 15.933 in the floor exercise.
After waiting for the final score to be provided, Raisman gave Biles a gentle hug. Biles cried when she knew she had achieved the score that she had dreamed for.
Raisman’s performance seems to be an act of vengeance for four years ago when she lost to Mustafina, who was then ranked third, during the finals game.
But this time, the 22-year old captain who has been laughably called “grandmother” by the Americans have gained a massive lead.
After the floor event, she blew a kiss to the crowd to announce her return. However, such a return look rather doubtful sometimes in the past.
Biles is just 19 years old. Since earlier this week, the news has gone viral on Twitter. For Biles, her life has taken on a whole new meaning.
